e.  once at the top of the stairs, head straight until you reach a wall.  staying near the wall, now head to your left.  the first room you see is the bedroom.  i had a scorned banshee up when i went through there the first time but you can avoid it easily enough.  the nightstand is over on the far side of the room, on your right hand side.  if the book is laying there, grab it and instant-gate out.  if your using a thurg potion with the casting time, sneak over to the southeast corner of the room (opposite the nightstand and around the bed), wait for the scorned banshee to finish pacing the room and once it's back on the far side of the room, click the potion.  you should have plenty of time to gate out this way and not attract any unwanted attention.  if the book isn't up, this corner also seems to be the safest place i found to camp out and return to later.  just be ready to hit hide &amp; sneak as soon as you appear back in game.<br>
<br>
full gear run!  woot!  best time i've had in game yet!<br>
<br>
Tillaini D'Sombras<br>
